.DT
add_spell
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_spell

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_spell -  This method adds a spell to a living object's known spells mapping
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_spell(string name,
mixed ob,
mixed func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the spell that can be used to access the
spell while casting
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the actual spell object
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - a spell function (unused?)
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the spell was added successfully, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/spells.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a spell to a living object's known spells mapping
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
player->add_spell("Ethereal Light", "/obj/spells/ethereal_light");

.EI

